#: ../../deployment/mlx_audio.rst:3 857bcd3ddac644a79c65d0ac7ccbca2f
msgid "MLX-Audio"
msgstr "MLX-Audio"

#: ../../deployment/mlx_audio.rst:5 c8eaafb3aadb4e45a14897f7fc2d21e6
msgid ""
"MLX-Audio is an audio framework built on `Apple MLX <https://github.com/ml-"
"explore/mlx>`_ for **Apple Silicon** Macs. It supports VoxCPM as one of its "
"TTS backends, and gives you a CLI, an OpenAI-compatible FastAPI server, and "
"a separate Next.js web UI."
msgstr ""
"MLX-Audio 是基于 `Apple MLX <https://github.com/ml-explore/mlx>`_ 的音频框架，面向 "
"**Apple Silicon** Mac。它将 VoxCPM 作为 TTS 后端之一，并提供 CLI、兼容 OpenAI 的 FastAPI "
"服务，以及独立的 Next.js Web 界面。"

#: ../../deployment/mlx_audio.rst:7 c9192c459ca14320b9827192d1a7aab6
msgid "Repo: `Blaizzy/mlx-audio <https://github.com/Blaizzy/mlx-audio>`_"
msgstr "仓库：`Blaizzy/mlx-audio <https://github.com/Blaizzy/mlx-audio>`_"

#: ../../deployment/mlx_audio.rst:10 cbbacdfef607472aae85a9d9e724baef
msgid ""
"This is a good fit if you want to run VoxCPM on an Apple Silicon Mac through"
" the MLX stack, especially when you also want a local API server or a "
"browser UI."
msgstr "若你想在 Apple Silicon Mac 上通过 MLX 栈运行 VoxCPM，且同时需要本地 API 服务或浏览器界面，这是较合适的选择。"

#: ../../deployment/mlx_audio.rst:12 bcb62d4f57784232aaa5913760332677
msgid "Supported VoxCPM Versions"
msgstr "支持的 VoxCPM 版本"

#: ../../deployment/mlx_audio.rst:16 172ca16c3b094f2a8bdb36592399ca32
msgid "VoxCPM 1.0 (0.5B)"
msgstr "VoxCPM 1.0（0.5B）"

