msgid "Python 3.10+"
msgstr "Python 3.10+"

#: ../../deployment/mlx_audio.rst:28 1555d7f0827943c499522841a003b877
msgid "``mlx`` and ``mlx-audio`` installed"
msgstr "已安装 ``mlx`` 与 ``mlx-audio``"

#: ../../deployment/mlx_audio.rst:31 f2acb9ad8df54cb8a369fd06cf5a0b31
msgid "Installation"
msgstr "安装"

#: ../../deployment/mlx_audio.rst:37 89bcfe0a2eda467d87a877910048fe4d
msgid "Or from source:"
msgstr "或从源码安装："

#: ../../deployment/mlx_audio.rst:46 0677280d487e4999917acabfffa90e3c
msgid "CLI Usage"
msgstr "命令行用法"

#: ../../deployment/mlx_audio.rst:48 0b4ec066973a4e17b32b0b2f14ce4430
msgid "Generate speech directly from the command line:"
msgstr "在命令行直接生成语音："

#: ../../deployment/mlx_audio.rst:54 f05fb2496fa846b0ab086d187e13df90
msgid ""
"The ``--model`` flag accepts ``voxcpm`` (maps to VoxCPM 1.0) or "
"``voxcpm1.5``."
msgstr "``--model`` 可接受 ``voxcpm``（对应 VoxCPM 1.0）或 ``voxcpm1.5``。"

#: ../../deployment/mlx_audio.rst:57 6f89ff8a13f441818526a8c16950feed
msgid "API Server"
msgstr "API 服务"

#: ../../deployment/mlx_audio.rst:59 78fa9df148b440dcb8c73e4a6ab2e0a9
msgid "MLX-Audio includes an OpenAI-compatible FastAPI server:"
msgstr "MLX-Audio 包含兼容 OpenAI 的 FastAPI 服务："

#: ../../deployment/mlx_audio.rst:65 e3515c286e0f4a439197883be00711f6
msgid ""
"This starts a local server that accepts ``/v1/audio/speech`` requests, "
"compatible with the OpenAI TTS API format. You can point any OpenAI-"
"compatible client at it."
msgstr ""
"这会启动一个本地服务，可接收 ``/v1/audio/speech`` 请求，格式与 OpenAI TTS API 兼容。可将任意兼容 OpenAI "
"的客户端指向该服务。"

#: ../../deployment/mlx_audio.rst:68 22c4a88e0547498baad60bd79ee192c4
msgid "Web UI"
msgstr "网页界面"

#: ../../deployment/mlx_audio.rst:70 6ed9d22c3f3a472b96337e85fe4b7944
msgid ""
"A separate Next.js web UI is included under ``mlx_audio/ui/``. See the `MLX-"
"Audio README <https://github.com/Blaizzy/mlx-audio#web-ui>`_ for setup "
"instructions."
msgstr ""
"独立的 Next.js Web 界面位于 ``mlx_audio/ui/``。搭建步骤见 `MLX-Audio README "
"<https://github.com/Blaizzy/mlx-audio#web-ui>`_。"

#: ../../deployment/mlx_audio.rst:73 6dd7491778ac40ed8bf687ee3c9add5a
msgid "Limitations"
msgstr "限制说明"

#: ../../deployment/mlx_audio.rst:75 53ee11b96cc2478497a7a691309a09f6
msgid ""
"VoxCPM 2 support is not yet available in MLX-Audio. The current backend "
"covers VoxCPM 1.0 and 1.5."
msgstr "MLX-Audio 尚未支持 VoxCPM 2。当前后端覆盖 VoxCPM 1.0 与 1.5。"

#: ../../deployment/mlx_audio.rst:76 70e0ec729b3643779093405391f0eb85
msgid ""
"Performance depends on your Apple Silicon chip. M1 Pro / M1 Max and later "
"provide the best experience."
msgstr "性能取决于你的 Apple Silicon 芯片。M1 Pro / M1 Max 及更新机型体验更佳。"

#: ../../deployment/mlx_audio.rst:77 bf98d13485e348eaa13af8bd49cbf820
msgid ""
"The MLX-Audio project is community-maintained and not officially affiliated "
"with OpenBMB."
msgstr "MLX-Audio 由社区维护，与 OpenBMB 无官方隶属关系。"

